main_components_overview_popup_one_conte: The strength of each vote, which is the sum of both staked CPU and NET of this account and any other account which has set this account as a proxy.
main_components_overview_popup_two_conte: The relative strength of the current vote against the strength of a vote cast today. The strength can be increased to 100% simply by casting your vote again.
main_components_overview_popup_three_con: The proxy set by this account. The staked voting weight is transfered from the current account and given to the proxy.
